title: What level of Bronze did I get myself into?
body:
[](http://media-cache-ec0.pinimg.com/736x/64/b4/fc/64b4fcd2001279546e381d65636286f4.jpg)

This *should* go in Memes and Games because I cannot for the life of me take this ending seriously (Moderator instantly deleted it though, despite it clearly not belonging here). It was Ranked, and I'm Silver 2, but this? This must have been Bronze level play...

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j5Zl8-DMEUw

From Outer Tower to Nexus Killed in 1:30, with only one person even trying to defend... who we killed on the way into the base...

http://matchhistory.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-details/NA1/2518995752/42592968?tab=overview

replies.body: I know, right? Braum, Ashe, and Evelyn I can *kinda* understand not wanting to back, because they can potentially race us, but where was Ahri?

Why would they keep going is the real question obviously someone stopped their push into the base while yall was going and see no one was there to stop yall.  

Idk if they thought irelia could stop yall even tho she already died once to that push lol.
